description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 arranged songs, navigators, and avatars from Touhou Project ~Ancient Temple!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Cristalize!
・IN MY LIFE
・DOWN DOWN DOLL
・My Voice is Dead.
・Colors
・hutatsu no tamashi wo tsurugi ni takushite
・The Justice Called "Innocence"
・Dance in the Blue Sky, Ink-Black Cherry Blossom
・Border of Colour
・？？？（Secret）

■Navigator
・Youmu Konpaku
・Yukari Yakumo

■Avatar
・YOUMU(3D)
・CHEN(2D)
・YUYUKO(2D)
・YUKARI.Y (2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Touhou Project Arrangements Pack 2
